msgstr "11. Применимое право"

#: templates/pages/core/transport_terms.html:120
msgid ""
"These Transport Terms are governed by the laws of the Russian Federation and "
"applicable international transportation conventions and agreements. Any "
"disputes shall be resolved in accordance with applicable legal procedures."
